<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博市场</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/markets/</link><description>彭博市场</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 07:03:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>油价上涨后英国通胀仍高于预期</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/oil-price-jump-leaves-uk-s-inflation-rate-higher-than-expected</link><description>由于油价上涨抵消了食品成本的下行压力，英国 9 月份通胀未能如预期放缓。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 06:09:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/oil-price-jump-leaves-uk-s-inflation-rate-higher-than-expected</guid></item><item><title>新加坡将检查瑞信等重大丑闻</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/singapore-to-inspect-credit-suisse-others-in-2-billion-scandal</link><description>瑞士信贷集团 (Credit Suisse Group AG) 至少一名客户在震惊新加坡的丑闻中被指控洗钱，新加坡金融监管机构将对瑞士信贷集团 (Credit Suisse Group AG) 进行现场检查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 02:40:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/singapore-to-inspect-credit-suisse-others-in-2-billion-scandal</guid></item><item><title>半导体行业整体下滑，ASML 订单大幅下滑</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/asml-orders-plunge-amid-wider-semiconductor-slump-video</link><description>由于半导体行业全行业低迷，阿斯麦第三季度的订单量大幅下降，推动中国销售额占其营收的近一半。阿普尔·罗奇在阿姆斯特丹接受彭博电视台报道。 （来源：彭博社）</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 06:50:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/asml-orders-plunge-amid-wider-semiconductor-slump-video</guid></item><item><title>中国和中东局势拖累股市下跌；英镑上涨：市场结束</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-17/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link><description>由于中东紧张局势加剧，亚洲股市下跌，且数据显示美国和英国央行利率制定者可能需要采取更多措施来控制通胀。对中国房地产行业的担忧掩盖了好于预期的经济数据。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 22:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-17/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid></item><item><title>三分钟了解市场：中国房地产对市场的影响将更长</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/markets-in-3-minutes-china-property-to-weigh-longer-on-markets</link><description>马克·库德莫尔 (Mark Cudmore) 和安娜·爱德华兹 (Anna Edwards) 在“彭博今日市场”上为分析师和投资者分析了今天的关键主题。 （来源：彭博社）</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 06:43:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/markets-in-3-minutes-china-property-to-weigh-longer-on-markets</guid></item><item><title>CVC Capital 考虑竞购欧洲支付巨头 Nexi</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-17/cvc-capital-said-to-weigh-bid-for-8-billion-payments-firm-nexi</link><description>知情人士称，CVC Capital Partners 正处于考虑对欧洲支付公司 Nexi SpA 进行潜在收购的早期阶段。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 17:16:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-17/cvc-capital-said-to-weigh-bid-for-8-billion-payments-firm-nexi</guid></item><item><title>中国批准转基因玉米和大豆种子品种以促进作物增产</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/china-approves-gm-corn-and-soybean-seed-varieties-in-crop-boost</link><description>中国已批准种植数十种转基因玉米和大豆种子品种，这是一项突破性举措，最终可能提高产量并减少对外国供应的依赖。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 02:55:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/china-approves-gm-corn-and-soybean-seed-varieties-in-crop-boost</guid></item><item><title>Le Maire 表示 TotalEnergies 将把法国燃油上限延长至 2024 年</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/le-maire-totalenergies-to-extend-french-fuel-cap-through-2024</link><description>法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔表示，TotalEnergies SE 将把法国加油站柴油和汽油每升 1.99 欧元的上限延长至 2024 年。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 06:10:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/le-maire-totalenergies-to-extend-french-fuel-cap-through-2024</guid></item><item><title>印度延长食糖出口限制将导致供应紧张</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/india-s-extension-of-sugar-export-curbs-set-to-tighten-supply</link><description>根据周三印度对外贸易总局的通知，印度将对食糖出口的限制延长至 10 月 31 日之后，此举可能会收紧全球供应。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 06:07:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/india-s-extension-of-sugar-export-curbs-set-to-tighten-supply</guid></item><item><title>必和必拓将以 32 亿美元的价格将焦煤矿出售给 Whitehaven</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-17/whitehaven-to-buy-two-bhp-coal-mines-in-queensland-afr-says</link><description>必和必拓集团有限公司 (BHP Group Ltd.) 同意以至少 32 亿美元的价格向 Whitehaven Coal Ltd. 出售两个澳大利亚炼焦煤业务，这家全球最大的矿业公司扩大了对化石燃料的退出。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 21:32:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-17/whitehaven-to-buy-two-bhp-coal-mines-in-queensland-afr-says</guid></item><item><title>彭博黎明：中东和非洲 10/18/2023</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/bloomberg-daybreak-middle-east-africa-10-18-2023-video</link><description>《黎明中东和非洲》是您每日关注的世界上发展最快的地区之一的焦点。我们在迪拜现场直播，为您带来最新的全球市场和分析，以及新闻采访，特别关注 MEA。当您前往海湾的办公室、在香港停下来吃午餐、或者在伦敦或约翰内斯堡开始新的一天时，所有这些以及更多。 （来源：彭博社）</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 06:01:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/bloomberg-daybreak-middle-east-africa-10-18-2023-video</guid></item><item><title>壳牌与卡塔尔签署荷兰为期 27 年的液化天然气供应协议</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/shell-and-qatar-sign-27-year-lng-supply-deal-for-netherlands</link><description>壳牌公司同意向荷兰购买卡塔尔液化天然气，为期 27 年，这是这个海湾国家在 2050 年之后向欧洲供应化石燃料的第二份重大合同。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 05:27:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/shell-and-qatar-sign-27-year-lng-supply-deal-for-netherlands</guid></item><item><title>交通部长表示，欧盟对中国电动汽车关税的计划可能会损害德国</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/eu-plan-for-china-ev-tariffs-could-hurt-germany-transport-minister-says</link><description>德国交通部长表示，如果欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收额外的进口关税，任何保护主义举措都可能遭到报复，德国可能会遭受损失。 “德国经济依赖于开放市场，”沃尔克·维辛在接受彭博社阿吉·坎特里尔采访时表示。 （来源：彭博社）</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 05:59:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/eu-plan-for-china-ev-tariffs-could-hurt-germany-transport-minister-says</guid></item><item><title>加沙医院爆炸加剧地区紧张局势，油价上涨</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-17/oil-jumps-as-gaza-hospital-blast-ratchets-up-regional-tensions</link><description>在总统乔·拜登抵达该地区之前，加沙一家医院发生致命爆炸，加剧了中东的紧张局势，油价上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 23:26:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-17/oil-jumps-as-gaza-hospital-blast-ratchets-up-regional-tensions</guid></item><item><title>事实证明，英国通胀略高于预期：今日市场</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2023-10-18/inflation-cpi-pound-boe-ftse-100-gilt-coverage-uk-markets-today</link><description>2023 年 9 月 19 日星期二，购物者前往英国伦敦斯特拉特福车站。根据中位数，将于周三公布的英国通胀数据可能会显示，上个月物价涨幅从 7 月份的 6.8% 升至 7%彭博社调查中的 30 多项估计。摄影师：霍莉·亚当斯/彭博社</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 05:42:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2023-10-18/inflation-cpi-pound-boe-ftse-100-gilt-coverage-uk-markets-today</guid></item><item><title>权威并不总是获胜。以市场为例</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2023-10-18/free-markets-how-authoritarianism-really-is-bad-for-stocks</link><description>&lt;p&gt;如果排除大宗商品和“资源诅咒”，那么自由民主经济的回报很容易击败威权制度。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 05:23:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2023-10-18/free-markets-how-authoritarianism-really-is-bad-for-stocks</guid></item><item><title>建筑商称不太可能付款后碧桂园违约迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/country-garden-on-verge-of-first-default-amid-silence-on-bond</link><description>陷入困境的中国建筑商碧桂园控股有限公司表示，随着美元债券利息宽限期结束，该公司将首次违约，这是震动中国金融市场的危机深化的最新迹象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 03:27:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/country-garden-on-verge-of-first-default-amid-silence-on-bond</guid></item><item><title>随着中东冲突加剧金价攀升至四周高位</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/gold-xauusd-edges-up-on-haven-demand-as-mideast-conflict-intensifies</link><description>由于中东冲突加剧提振了避险需求，加上加沙发生致命爆炸后，外交解决方案的希望不断恶化，金价跃升至四个星期以来的最高水平。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 01:15:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/gold-xauusd-edges-up-on-haven-demand-as-mideast-conflict-intensifies</guid></item><item><title>习近平希望重振“一带一路”倡议</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/xi-looks-to-reinvigorate-belt-and-road-initiative</link><description>中国国家主席习近平为其旗舰“一带一路”倡议辩护，将这一价值1万亿美元的计划视为全球增长的驱动力，同时表示那些将其视为威胁的人正在给自己带来伤害。 “只有世界好，中国才能好。”周三，习近平在北京人民大会堂举行第三届“一带一路”高峰论坛开幕式、纪念其标志性项目十周年时表示。 “中国做得好，世界就会变得更好。” （来源：彭博社）</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 05:02:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/xi-looks-to-reinvigorate-belt-and-road-initiative</guid></item><item><title>开始新的一天需要知道的五件事</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-10-18/stock-markets-today-biden-s-trip-oil-rallies-china-s-gdp-wall-street-s-focus</link><description>&lt;p&gt;了解市场的最新动态&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 05:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-10-18/stock-markets-today-biden-s-trip-oil-rallies-china-s-gdp-wall-street-s-focus</guid></item><item><title>马科斯暂停菲律宾财富基金以确保保障</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-17/marcos-suspends-philippine-wealth-fund-implementation-inquirer</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯 (Ferdinand Marcos Jr.) 已暂停执行一项创建该国首个主权财富基金的法律，因为提供资金的国营银行之一正在寻求央行的监管救济。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 22:55:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-17/marcos-suspends-philippine-wealth-fund-implementation-inquirer</guid></item><item><title>以色列的货币防御正在将焦点从降息上转移</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-17/israel-s-currency-defense-takes-priority-as-rate-cut-bets-fizzle</link><description>以色列央行强调了在谢克尔跌至八年低点后稳定谢克尔的紧迫性，这改变了押注下周将大幅降息的经济学家和交易员的预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 14:01:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-17/israel-s-currency-defense-takes-priority-as-rate-cut-bets-fizzle</guid></item><item><title>彭博市场：中国公开赛 2023 年 10 月 18 日</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/bloomberg-markets-china-open-10-18-2023-video</link><description>《彭博市场：中国公开赛》是香港和内地市场的权威指南。 David Ingles 和 Yvonne Man 为您带来最新新闻和分析，帮助您为交易日做好准备。在 120 多个国家/地区的 2700 多名记者和分析师的支持下，我们为您提供将影响该地区市场的全球故事。 （来源：彭博社）</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 04:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/bloomberg-markets-china-open-10-18-2023-video</guid></item><item><title>电影制片人奥尼尔谈印度同性婚姻权利裁决</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/filmmaker-onir-on-india-same-sex-marriage-rights-ruling-video</link><description>印度电影导演奥尼尔分享了他对印度最高法院对同性婚姻权利的判决的反应。他与 Rishaad Salamat 和 Yvonne Man 就“彭博市场：亚洲”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 04:15:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/filmmaker-onir-on-india-same-sex-marriage-rights-ruling-video</guid></item><item><title>清华大学朱教授谈中国经济展望</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/tsinghua-university-s-zhu-on-china-s-economic-outlook-video</link><description>清华大学国家金融研究院副院长朱宁探讨中国经济前景和风险。他与 Rishaad Salamat 和 Yvonne Man 就“彭博市场：亚洲”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 04:02:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-10-18/tsinghua-university-s-zhu-on-china-s-economic-outlook-video</guid></item><item><title>气候变化正在推动你看不见的全球水贸易</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2023-water-data-trade-climate-change/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;更加极端的天气正在重塑水的供应，而水是国际市场上几乎所有买卖产品中不可或缺的商品。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 04:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2023-water-data-trade-climate-change/</guid></item><item><title>标准银行表示，乌干达 40 亿美元管道项目即将做出决定</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/uganda-s-4-billion-pipeline-near-financial-close-standard-bank-says</link><description>标准银行集团表示，一条连接乌干达和坦桑尼亚、耗资 40 亿美元、颇受争议的原油管道已经克服了推迟最终决定的关键障碍。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/uganda-s-4-billion-pipeline-near-financial-close-standard-bank-says</guid></item><item><title>梅洛尼为意大利在一系列评级审查中的清算做好准备</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/meloni-braces-for-italy-s-reckoning-in-cascade-of-rating-reviews</link><description>随着意大利 2024 年预算案落下帷幕，现在是时候阅读评论了。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/meloni-braces-for-italy-s-reckoning-in-cascade-of-rating-reviews</guid></item><item><title>德意志银行新星升职后面临危机</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/deutsche-bank-s-rising-star-faces-unit-in-crisis-after-promotion</link><description>当克劳迪奥·德·桑克蒂斯 (Claudio de Sanctis) 于 7 月份晋升为德意志银行 (Deutsche Bank AG) 庞大的德国零售业务主管时，他立即做出了自己的贡献。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/deutsche-bank-s-rising-star-faces-unit-in-crisis-after-promotion</guid></item><item><title>中国要求银行在紧缩时期扩大地方政府贷款</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/china-tells-banks-to-extend-local-government-loans-amid-crunch</link><description>中国金融监管机构要求政策性银行和最大的贷款机构发行新贷款，以覆盖今年和2024年到期的地方政府发行的离岸债务，加大力度缓解高负债城市的信贷紧缩。</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 03:43:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-18/china-tells-banks-to-extend-local-government-loans-amid-crunch</guid></item></channel></rss>